OL,3,CUnanimous vote to ban disposable vapes
OL,4,Cin Jersey
OL,6,FJersey politicians have unanimously
OL,7,Fvoted to ban disposable vapes in the
OL,8,Fisland.
OL,10,FThe States Assembly unanimously agreed
OL,11,Fto amend an existing law on Wednesday
OL,12,F11 December, with 45 votes for and 0
OL,13,Fagainst.
OL,15,FIt brings the island in line with the
OL,16,FUK, which will enact new legislation
OL,17,Fto ban the sale of single-use vapes
OL,18,Ffrom 1 June 2025.
