OL,3,CUnanimous vote to ban disposable vapes
OL,4,Cin Jersey
OL,6,FSelling, importing and supplying
OL,7,Fdisposable vapes also became a
OL,8,Fcriminal offence in Guernsey in April
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FThe amendment to the Single-Use
OL,12,FPlastics etc. (Restrictions) (Jersey)
OL,13,FLaw - originally enacted in 2022 -
OL,14,Fadds single-use vapes to the list of
OL,15,Frestricted items.
OL,17,FIt hopes to reduce the number of young
OL,18,Fpeople vaping, with a recent study by
OL,19,FPublic Health Jersey revealing that
OL,20,Fmore than 95% of local children who
OL,21,Fvape opt for single-use devices.
