OL,3,CUnanimous vote to ban disposable vapes
OL,4,Cin Jersey
OL,6,FThe proposition, put forward by
OL,7,FInfrastructure Minister Constable Andy
OL,8,FJehan and Environment Minister Deputy
OL,9,FSteve Luce, states that banning the
OL,10,Fdevices will bring environmental
OL,11,Fbenefits and reduce waste.
OL,13,FConstable Jehan told ITV News: "I
OL,14,Fthink we've got far too many of these
OL,15,Fproducts which are just disposed of in
OL,16,Fthe street, in hedges.
OL,18,F"Also, when we collect them, it gives
OL,19,Fus a problem in terms of the lithium
OL,20,Fbatteries not being disposed of
OL,21,Fcorrectly so they could cause a fire.
